properties.Hours: Lloyd parking meters east of NE Grand Avenue operate from 8 a.m. to 6 p.m., Monday through Saturday, unless otherwise posted.  Meters on and west of NE Grand Avenue operate from 8 a.m. to 10 p.m., Monday through Saturday, unless otherwise posted.
Marquam Hill parking meters operate from 8 a.m. to 6 p.m., Monday through Friday, unless otherwise posted.
Downtown parking meters operate from 8 a.m. to 7 p.m., Monday through Saturday, and from 1 p.m. to 7 p.m. on Sunday, unless otherwise posted.
Northwest District parking meters are located on and around NW 21st and NW 23rd and operate from 9:00 AM – 7:00 PM on Monday through Saturday unless otherwise posted.
Central Eastside parking meters operate from 8 a.m. to 6 p.m., Monday through Friday, unless otherwise posted.
